&lt;h1 id=&quot;build&quot;&gt;Build&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;
&lt;pre data-lang=&quot;chatlink&quot; class=&quot;language-chatlink z-code&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-chatlink&quot; data-lang=&quot;chatlink&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-source z-chatlink&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-definition z-string z-begin&quot;&gt;[&amp;amp;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;DQgCHhM&#x2F;Ii6bAAAAcAEAAOQAAAAPEwAAlQAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA=&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-definition z-string z-end&quot;&gt;]&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;div data-armory-embed=&#x27;skills&#x27; data-armory-ids=&#x27;10547,10589,10541,30772,10646&#x27;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;&lt;div data-armory-embed=&#x27;specializations&#x27; data-armory-ids=&#x27;2,19,34&#x27; data-armory-2-traits=&#x27;857,855,842&#x27; data-armory-19-traits=&#x27;1876,1844,778&#x27; data-armory-34-traits=&#x27;2020,2031,1919&#x27;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;notes&quot;&gt;Notes&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Spawn all minions to distract enemies&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Go into &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;30792&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Reaper&#x27;s Shroud, drop an ice field with &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;30557&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Executioner&#x27;s Scythe&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;30504&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Soul Spiral in the ice field&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;When out of shroud, use &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;30772&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; &quot;Rise!&quot; when you can hit at least 3 enemies, and then build life force&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;When your minions die, they will spawn poison fields due to &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;traits&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;842&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Death Nova. Poison application also grants Carapace as well as causing some damage and inhibiting enemy healing.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Try to combo &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;30504&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Soul Spiral in the poison fields to create additional poison bolts&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use the Bone Minion&#x27;s flipover skill, &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10540&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Putrid Explosion, to quickly generate fields. This is also a blast finisher.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&quot;open-world-tagging&quot;&gt;Open World Tagging&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;If you&#x27;re in a large group PvE environment, swap to staff to tag lots of targets&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;With &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;traits&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;778&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Transfusion traited, staff will buff all allies. This includes your minions&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Staff also brings more opportunites to inflict bleeding to proc &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;traits&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;1876&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Blood Bond, essentially giving life steal to allies&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&quot;condition-cleanse&quot;&gt;Condition Cleanse&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Swap &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;traits&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;855&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Deadly Strength to &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;traits&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;858&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Necromantic Corruption to allow your minions to strip conditions from you
and transfer them to enemies. This is incredibly good in high condi fights like Slothasar. Note that each minion has an independent 10
second cooldown. Mass minion summons like &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;30772&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; &quot;Rise!&quot; will stack those cooldowns, so it can be advantageous to spread
&lt;em&gt;other&lt;&#x2F;em&gt; summons out if possible.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&quot;crowd-control&quot;&gt;Crowd Control&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You have many options:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;29855&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Nightfall (Greatword 4)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;29740&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Grasping Darkness (Greatsword 5)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10605&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Chillblains (Staff 3)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;19115&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Reaper&#x27;s Mark (Staff 5)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;49794&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Executioner&#x27;s Scythe (Shroud 5)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;29709&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Terrify (Shroud 3 flipover)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10647&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Charge (Flesh Golem flipover)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;10590&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Haunt (Shadow Fiend flipover)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
